_sText:
The map has 56 player slots.. but I would recommend about 20 or so due to its an aim map and kinda detailed so it might drop FPS on low-end computers.

Two of the models were taken (with an OK) from: Ecplise Mod for HL2.

STORY:

A group of angry miners have decided to take over the
Amwoods mine in northern California.  They are threatening
to close it and destroy the entrance to the mine
sealing the mine owners inside. They have now taken up
arms and are guarding the mine with their lives.  

A group of Counter-Terrorists have been dispatched to
apprehend the group of angry miners.  The counter-terrorists
have arrived and now the battle starts!
